      <trans-unit id="start.status_description" datatype="html">
        <source> Hieronder volg je eenvoudig de status van jouw project.<x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/><x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/> Het stappenplan biedt direct inzicht in waar we ons in het proces bevinden, welke taken zijn afgerond en wat de volgende stappen zijn.<x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/><x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/> Zo ben je altijd volledig geïnformeerd over de voortgang. </source>
        <target> Below you can easily follow the status of your project.<x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/><x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/> The step-by-step plan provides direct insight into where we are in the process, which tasks have been completed and what the next steps are.<x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/><x id="LINE_BREAK" ctype="lb" equiv-text="&lt;br&gt;"/> This way you are always fully informed about the progress. </target>
